cset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Simon-Cowell-Liam-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814446" class="wp-caption-text">西蒙·考威尔（右）和劳伦·西尔弗曼。图片来源：尼尔·霍兰。图片来源：贾斯汀·塔利斯/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>佩恩的灵柩乘坐一辆白色马拉灵车抵达圣玛丽教堂，上面有拼写着“儿子”和“爸爸”的鲜花致敬，还有其他鲜花致敬，其中包括保龄球瓶和球形状的鲜花，参考了佩恩的一个最喜欢的活动。仪式结束后，四名抬棺人将棺材抬出教堂，后面跟着佩恩的父母和谢丽尔。</p><p>虽然一小群当地人聚集在教堂外，但粉丝们普遍远离仪式。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814447" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814447" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814447" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩的葬礼上，抬棺者抬着他的棺材" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Payne-Coffin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814447" class="wp-caption-text">葬礼结束后，抬棺人将利亚姆·佩恩的灵柩抬出圣玛丽教堂。图片来源：贾斯汀·塔利斯/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3814448" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814448" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loadin