atures/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755"><em>NME</em>将佩恩描述为“帮助引发流行现象的一个单向明星”，</a>并补充说：“令人钦佩的坦率和不断向前迈进的渴望只是他遗产的一部分。佩恩（Payne）在包括儿子熊（Bear）在内的家庭中幸存下来，他在使一个方向成为全球现象方面发挥了关键作用，他将一代年轻人变成了流行歌迷。随着一位在社交媒体时代名声的明星，他留下了音乐，模因和记忆，这些音乐，模因和记忆将在未来很多年被珍惜。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cheryl-one-direction-bandmates-and-simon-cowell-attend-liam-paynes-funeral-3814433">谢丽尔（Cheryl）邮政，一个方向的队友和西蒙·考威尔（Simon Cowell）参加了利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne）的葬礼，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
看看这些复古的鲍勃·迪伦风格的“完全未知”海报 - NME 独家https://www.nme.com/news/film/bob-dylan-timothee-chalamet-a-complete-unknown-posters-3814082?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bob-dylan-timothee-chalamet-a-complete-未知海报Ali ShutlerWed, 20 Nov 2024 16:00:36 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3814082 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet) 在《完全未知》片场饰演鲍勃·迪伦 (Bob Dylan)。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>以蒂莫西·查拉梅为民间传奇人物</p><p>这篇文章《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bob-dylan-timothee-chalamet-a-complete-unknown-posters-3814082">看看这些复古的鲍勃·迪伦灵感的“完全未知”海报——NME 独家》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet) 在《完全未知》片场饰演鲍勃·迪伦 (Bob Dylan)。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Timothee-Chalamet-on-set-22A-Complete-Unknown22-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>备受期待的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦</a>传记片<em>《完全未知》</em>讲述了 19 岁迪伦从斗志旺盛的民谣歌手迅速崛起为排行榜冠军的摇滚传奇人物的故事。</p><p>为庆祝这部电影由蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet) 饰演广受赞誉的游吟诗人，并于 1 月 17 日（美国 12 月 25 日）在英国影院上映，许多受迪伦最受欢迎的歌曲启发而专门设计的海报被制作出来。请在下面的<em>NME</em>上独家查看它们。</p><p> “我真的很想创作一系列海报，与电影、音乐和时代相得益彰，在风格上复古，并注入一些现代设计的元素，”设计师<a href="https://www.mattneedle.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">马特·尼德尔 (Matt Needle)</a>说。 “每件作品都是一个独立的设计作品，其灵感和主导来自于那首特定的歌曲，并与[歌曲中描述的]角色相关。”</p><p>这五张海报以身着全套服装的 Chalamet 为主角，灵感源自 1964 年充满政治色彩的经典歌曲《The Times They Are A-Changin》和 1965 年革命性的热门歌曲《Like A Rolling Stone》等歌曲。 </p><figure id="attachment_3813999" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813999" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813999" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2999" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone-1392x2087.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Like-A-Rolling-Stone-1068x1601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813999" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：探照灯影业</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3814000" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814000" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814000" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2999" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging-1392x2087.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Times-They-Are-Achanging-1068x1601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814000" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：探照灯影业</figcaption></figure><p>“最初，我尝试将 Timothée 的形象与 Dylan 的每次迭代相结合（早期、民谣、更风格化的西装和眼镜造型、二重唱和电子音乐）。当然，这一点在整个过程中不断演变，但蒂莫西的每张照片都拍摄得如此精美，构图如此，充满个性，以至于有大量的图像可供使用。我试图选择那些能够引导故事的不同元素并以动态和有趣的方式引导构图的元素，”Needle 继续说道。</p><p>海报还向早期单曲《Blowin&#39; In The Wind》致敬，该单曲与琼·贝兹 (Joan Baez) 一起演唱，并出现在 1963 年的《The Freewheelin&#39; Bob Dylan》和《Girl From The North Country》中。这首关于社区、理解和希望的优美歌曲最初作为鲍勃·迪伦第二张专辑的一部分发行，随后他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-cash">约翰尼·卡什</a>在 1969 年的《纳什维尔天际线》中重新录制了这首歌。 </p><figure id="attachment_3813998" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813998" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813998" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country.jpg" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 饰 鲍勃·迪伦" width="2000" height="2999" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country-1392x2087.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Girls-From-The-North-Country-1068x1601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813998" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：探照灯影业</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3813997" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813997" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813997" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind.jpg" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 饰 鲍勃·迪伦" width="2000" height="2999" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind-1392x2087.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Unknown-poster-Blowin-In-The-Wind-1068x1601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813997" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：探照灯影业</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3813996" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813996" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813996" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues.jpg" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 饰 鲍勃·迪伦" width="2000" height="2999" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues-1392x2087.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/A-Complete-Uknown-poster-Subterranean-homesick-blues-1068x1601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813996" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：探照灯影业</figcaption></figure><p>在谈到通过海报系列向迪伦及其遗产致敬时，尼德尔说：“这些图像旨在标记迪伦的不同方面。因此，我们有《风中飘》和《来自北国的女孩》来纪念早年的岁月，《像滚石》涵盖了旅行和巡演，《地下思乡布鲁斯》表达了抗议，《Times They Are A-》改变他的电动阶段。设计中融入的镜头与这些主题/歌词非常契合，同时也唤起了迪伦过去几年的一些标志性形象。”</p><p>柴勒梅德与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edward-norton">爱德华·诺顿</a>（皮特·西格饰）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elle-fanning">艾丽·范宁</a>（西尔维·罗素，迪伦在纽约的第一个女友苏西·罗托洛的虚构版本，于 2011 年去世）一起主演了这部电影，该片改编自伊利亚·沃尔德 2015 年出版的书籍<em>《迪伦走向电动！》纽波特、西格、迪伦和六十年代分裂之夜。</em></p><p>迪伦作为执行制片人监督了该项目，据剧组人员称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bob-dylan-insisted-on-putting-one-totally-made-up-fact-into-biopic-a-complete-unknown-hes-such-a-troublemaker-3813783">迪伦要求至少包括一个完全不准确的时刻</a>。 “他真是个麻烦制造者，”诺顿说。</p><p>这篇文章《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bob-dylan-timothee-chalamet-a-complete-unknown-posters-3814082">看看这些复古的鲍勃·迪伦灵感的“完全未知”海报——NME 独家》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
臭名昭著的格拉斯哥旺卡经历背后的男子被列入性犯罪者名单https://www.nme.com/news/film/man-behind-inknown-glasgow-wonka-experience-put-on-sex-offenders-register-3814398?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=man-behind-inknown-格拉斯哥旺卡体验性犯罪者登记处Damian JonesWed, 20 Nov 2024 15:51:28 +0000 Film NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3814398 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威利·旺卡经历" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>比利·科尔因多次向一名女性发送露骨照片而被判犯有虐待行为</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/man-behind-infamous-glasgow-wonka-experience-put-on-sex-offenders-register-3814398">臭名昭著的格拉斯哥旺卡经历背后的男人被列入性犯罪者名册的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威利·旺卡经历" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wonkaglasgow_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格拉斯哥旺卡事件背后的男子已被列入性犯罪者名册。</p><p>周一（11 月 18 日），比利·库尔因多次向一名女性发送露骨照片而被格拉斯哥治安法院判定犯有虐待行为。</p><p>法院获悉，这位前慈善工人在三月份以错误的名字从Facebook帐户中给该名女子发了电话。据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crmz1x3y7mxo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司新闻</em></a>报道，尽管她要求他停止，但他继续在 Snapchat 和 WhatsApp 上给她发消息，并多次称她为“性感”、“甜唇”和“我的小魅力”。</p><p>随后，库尔开始发送自己穿着内衣的照片以及更亲密的照片，并在向警方报告后被捕。</p><p>他的律师尼尔·斯图尔特告诉法庭，今年早些时候在格拉斯哥举行的旺卡活动失败后，库尔的精神健康状况“恶化”。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Timothee-Chalamet-Wonka.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">格拉斯哥旺卡体验的灵感来自于 Timothée Chalamet 主演的热门电影《旺卡》 (Wonka) 图片来源：华纳兄弟娱乐公司、Jaap Buittendijk</figcaption></figure><p>广告宣传为“甜蜜和想象力的庆典”，其灵感来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅</a>主演的热门电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka"><i>《旺卡》</i></a>和该片背后的罗尔德·达尔的书籍，愤怒的家长在上映后不久就开始要求退款，称其为一场“闹剧” “牛仔”。</p><p>一部一次性纪录片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/willy-wonka-experience-documentary-to-air-on-channel-5-3598154"><i>《旺卡：震惊英国的丑闻</i></a>》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/flop-willy-wonka-experience-in-glasgow-goes-viral-for-being-so-terrible-3593684">在社交媒体上疯传</a>后，在第五频道播出。科尔当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/willy-wonka-experience-organiser-says-his-life-has-been-ruined-3602390">表示，这种反应“毁了他的生活”</a> 。</p><p>这次活动引起了如此多的关注，好莱坞女演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sydney-sweeney-mocks-glasgows-wonka-experience-in-snl-skit-3596176">西德尼·斯威尼（Sydney Sweeney）甚至在她最近在<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目中表演的小品中对此进行了取笑</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/horror-movie-based-on-glasgow-willy-wonka-experience-3596802">苏格兰电影制作公司 Kaledonia Pictures 委托拍摄了</a>一部根据这次失败的演习改编的恐怖电影<em>《未知》</em> 。</p><p>法官在宣判时表示，羁押门槛已经通过，但他可以采取替代羁押措施，并且给予库尔 120 小时的无薪工作和一年的监管。</p><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的更多帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="http://rapecrisis.org.uk/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/man-behind-infamous-glasgow-wonka-experience-put-on-sex-offenders-register-3814398">臭名昭著的格拉斯哥旺卡经历背后的男人被列入性犯罪者名册的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
